@RC - I don't get you calling me out for not being a factor in the game as scummy.<br>
So far in this game we've lynched one scum, and run up two claimed PRs (of which I presume you'll calim at least one is confirmed town <img class="smilies" src="./images/smilies/icon_wink.gif" width="15" height="15" alt=";)" title="Wink"> ) I opposed all three operations - so unless your claim is I'm scum playing hardcore pro-town to avoid lynch (and in which case, why not sheep me a bit, since clearly I'll be hard bussing too...) I don't get the point. Yeah, I haven't been part of any of the major operations that have happened, but that puts me on the town side of history as far as I can see - you disagree?

